Setup:

http://www.packer.io/   # install 0.6.0
http://www.vagrantup.com/ # install 1.5.4
https://www.virtualbox.org/ # install 4.3.10

To create a vagrant box:

# using collectd-librato-ubuntu-12.04 as an example

packer build -only=virtualbox-iso collectd-librato-ubuntu-12.04.json
(optional: vagrant box remove collectd-librato-ubuntu-12.04)
vagrant box add collectd-librato-ubuntu-12.04.4-0 collectd-librato-ubuntu-12.04.4-0.box
